## API Endpoints

| Method | URL | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | optional | Returns `{ id, name, email, picture }` or 401 |
| GET | `/api/auth/login-url` | none | Returns OAuth2 login path |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | session | Invalidates session |
| GET | `/api/history` | required | Get last 20 searches |
| POST | `/api/history` | required | Save a search entry |
| DELETE | `/api/history/{id}` | required | Delete a search entry |
